{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-index-jsx","path":"/post/novel/poetry-typhoon","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0e96350945d37c7c730587b8849902cc/c8407/cover.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.44171779141104%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"https://www.pexels.com/zh-tw/photo/268791/\"\n        title=\"https://www.pexels.com/zh-tw/photo/268791/\"\n        src=\"/static/0e96350945d37c7c730587b8849902cc/6aca1/cover.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0e96350945d37c7c730587b8849902cc/d2f63/cover.jpg 163w,\n/static/0e96350945d37c7c730587b8849902cc/c989d/cover.jpg 325w,\n/static/0e96350945d37c7c730587b8849902cc/6aca1/cover.jpg 650w,\n/static/0e96350945d37c7c730587b8849902cc/7c09c/cover.jpg 975w,\n/static/0e96350945d37c7c730587b8849902cc/01ab0/cover.jpg 1300w,\n/static/0e96350945d37c7c730587b8849902cc/c8407/cover.jpg 5500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>颱風</h3>\n<p>大雨未止，人不知，傾盆的哭泣怎能</p>\n<p>三夜連綿不停？</p>\n<p>雨水千線紛飛</p>\n<p>她，不撐傘、沒戴帽</p>\n<p>太久未雨而開心的仰天長笑</p>\n<p>翩翩在原地起舞</p>\n<p><br></br></p>\n<p>振動衣袖拌水沉甸如撩</p>\n<p>她卻熱當蝴蝶的翅膀</p>\n<p>散髮迴旋地飛越</p>\n<p>一地水鄉澤國</p>\n<p><br></br></p>\n<p>髪絲猶如雨絲</p>\n<p>她掂腳尖、扭蛇腰，一個轉身</p>\n<p>烏黑的頭髮成為墨然雨條</p>\n<p>混在一起了，那雨和髪</p>\n<p>或是</p>\n<p>垂直、平行，交織</p>\n<p>半壁山村的泥土，彷彿罾罟</p>\n<p>把村民</p>\n<p>一網打盡，徒留漏網之魚</p>\n<p><br></br></p>\n<p>她停下腳步，半隻腳踏進水裡</p>\n<p>風來浪起</p>\n<p>小樹林邊蜘蛛三代結網</p>\n<p>三秒汩沒河底</p>\n<p>有魚跳到腳邊，她捨起</p>\n<p>一股內疚的表情</p>\n<p>右跨一步</p>\n<p>水起，人分離</p>\n<p><br></br></p>\n<p>魚回不了河裡</p>\n<p>蜘蛛找不回樹林</p>\n<p>大雨未止，她不知，手中的生命既然來了又該</p>\n<p>向何處遠去？</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"August 12, 2009","slug":"/novel/poetry-typhoon","title":"詩 - 颱風","tags":"詩, 颱風","hot":false}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/novel/poetry-typhoon"}}}